      <div class="relative px-6 md:px-8 py-10 md:py-14 flex flex-col gap-3 items-start fade-up">
        <span class="font-display font-bold select-none -mb-6" style="font-size: clamp(72px, 10vw, 140px); line-height: 1; color: hsl(var(--primary) / 0.25);">02</span>
        <h3 class="font-display uppercase text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight text-white">Budujemy chatbota</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-white/65 leading-relaxed max-w-[28ch]">Tworzymy asystenta z pełną wiedzą o firmie — usługi, ceny, FAQ, godziny.</p>
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-20 right-0 h-px w-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, hsl(var(--border) / 0.3), transparent);"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative px-6 md:px-8 py-10 md:py-14 flex flex-col gap-3 items-start fade-up">
        <span class="font-display font-bold select-none -mb-6" style="font-size: clamp(72px, 10vw, 140px); line-height: 1; color: hsl(var(--primary) / 0.25);">03</span>
        <h3 class="font-display uppercase text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight text-white">Wdrożenie w 48h</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-white/65 leading-relaxed max-w-[28ch]">Gotowy skrypt — jeden kod na stronie i chatbot działa.</p>
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-20 right-0 h-px w-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, hsl(var(--border) / 0.3), transparent);"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative px-6 md:px-8 py-10 md:py-14 flex flex-col gap-3 items-start fade-up">
